snippet.title: Boom Voyage (2007) Full Playthrough - 2020
snippet.description:
I played this game a long time ago and had forgotten about it in the meantime. Sometime recently I rediscovered it and decided to play it again.
This game has many cool stages and plenty of cool bonuses similar to the Magic Ball series.
The graphics are pretty decent for a pc game from 2007 and the music fits each stage.
